title: The Artie Quitter Podcast JUL 08 2015 Wed.mp3
description:
After quitting the "Howard Stern Show," surviving a suicide attempt and hosting his own DirecTV program, comedian Artie Lange is venturing into a new frontier -- podcasting.
Co-Hosts for Artie include Comedians Joe Matarese, Gino Bisconti, Sue Costello  and Chris Cotton, which add to the vibe of hanging out with the guys -- talkin' sports and bustin' chops.


TODAY's SHOW

Artie is joined again by TV Writer, Comedian & Ex TV Sports Anchor/college hoops player Paul Morrissey.

Artie is amazed to discover that there is some recently uncovered audio from the Hindenberg disaster and a broadcaster who was also present. Jason Pierre Paul and his fireworks mishap is somehow involved
